---
// Closing CTA section - YPSM Jombang
---

<section class="bg-gradient-warm text-white py-20 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Arabic decorative quote -->
    <p class="font-arabic text-2xl text-white/15 mb-8 leading-loose" aria-hidden="true">
      &#x645;&#x646; &#x630;&#x622; &#x627;&#x644;&#x630;&#x64A; &#x64A;&#x642;&#x631;&#x636; &#x627;&#x644;&#x644;&#x647; &#x642;&#x631;&#x636;&#x64B;&#x627; &#x62D;&#x633;&#x646;&#x64B;&#x627; &#x641;&#x64A;&#x636;&#x627;&#x639;&#x641;&#x647; &#x644;&#x647; &#x623;&#x636;&#x639;&#x627;&#x641;&#x64B;&#x627; &#x643;&#x62B;&#x64A;&#x631;&#x629;
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 font-heading" data-i18n="cta.title">
      Mulai Donasi &amp; Jadi Bagian dari Perubahan
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-white/75 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-i18n="cta.subtitle">
      Setiap rupiah yang Anda donasikan akan menjadi cahaya bagi masa depan mereka
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-14">
      <button
        onclick="event.preventDefault();window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('campaign:donate',{detail:{campaign:'santunan-ikhlas',campaignLabel:'Santunan'}}))"
        data-i18n="cta.santunan.cta"
        class="border-2 border-secondary-500 text-secondary-300 hover:bg-secondary-500/20 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all"
      >
        Santunan
      </button>
      <button
        onclick="event.preventDefault();window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('campaign:donate',{detail:{campaign:'orang-tua-asuh',campaignLabel:'Orang Tua Asuh'}}))"
        data-i18n="cta.ota.cta"
        class="bg-coral-500 hover:bg-coral-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all"
      >
        Orang Tua Asuh
      </button>
      <button
        onclick="event.preventDefault();window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('campaign:donate',{detail:{campaign:'wakaf',campaignLabel:'Wakaf'}}))"
        data-i18n="cta.wakaf.cta"
        class="border-2 border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all"
      >
        Wakaf
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Newsletter signup -->
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <form class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 mb-4" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
        <input
          type="email"
          placeholder="Email Anda"
          required
          class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-primary-900 placeholder-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-secondary-500"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="bg-secondary-500 text-primary-900 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-secondary-400 transition-all whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          Dapatkan Update
        </button>
      </form>

      <label class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/60 cursor-pointer">
        <input type="checkbox" class="rounded border-white/30 bg-transparent" />
        <span>Saya setuju dihubungi via WA</span>
      </label>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-white/50 text-sm">
      Bergabung dengan 200+ donatur tetap
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
